dc_description_s: This data set shows the Rural/Urban Transition Area as designated on the comprehensive plan.Rural/Urban Transition Areas are designated Rural Residential (RR) or Rural Residential-5 (RR-5) by the comprehensive plan. These areas are outside of the Urban Growth Area (UGA) where certain urban-type evelopments may be permitted, while preserving the rural character of the area.Derivative data is routinely refreshed as the master data set is updated.
